  {
    "index": 3,
    "hash": "MH9jaszmU1TE3s42X3/kVW7fjo0=",
    "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:47.000Z",
    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "Two hierarchical manifests tier the on-Swarm layout below the per-document manifest.\n\n**User manifest** at `ph:v2:user:<eth_address>` indexes the user's drives (not individual docs):\n\n```json\n{\n  \"address\": \"0x1234...\",\n  \"beeNodePublicKey\": \"02abc...\",\n  \"documents\": {},\n  \"drives\": {\n    \"drive-xyz\": { \"name\": \"My Finance Drive\", \"documentIds\": [], \"lastUpdated\": \"...\" }\n  },\n  \"updatedAt\": \"...\"\n}\n```\n\n**Drive manifest** at `ph:v2:drive:<driveId>` lists documents and folders for that drive:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"driveId\": \"drive-xyz\",\n  \"name\": \"My Finance Drive\",\n  \"documents\": {\n    \"abc-123\": { \"documentType\": \"powerhouse/budget-statement\", \"name\": \"Q1 Budget\", \"parentFolder\": \"folder-1\", \"lastUpdated\": \"...\" }\n  },\n  \"folders\": {\n    \"folder-1\": { \"name\": \"Reports\" },\n    \"folder-2\": { \"name\": \"Subfolder\", \"parentFolder\": \"folder-1\" }\n  },\n  \"updatedAt\": \"...\"\n}\n```\n\nFolders are tracked by reading the drive's node tree on each flush; recovery restores them by executing `ADD_FOLDER` and `MOVE_NODE` actions.",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:47.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:47.000Z"
    }
  },
